Submitted on record and briefs February 21, reversed and remanded for new trial March 1, 1978 STATE OF OREGON, Respondent, v. THOMAS CHARLES DYKES, Appellant. (No. 76-29732-T, CA 9306) 575 P2d 176 Walter D. Nunley, Medford, filed the brief for appellant. James A. Redden, Attorney General, Al J. Laue, Solicitor General, and Catherine Allan, Assistant Attorney General, Salem, filed the brief for respondent.

Before Schwab, Chief Judge, and Lee, Richardson, and Joseph, Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Reversed and remanded for new trial. State v. Wiik, 31 Or App 571, 570 P2d 1021 (1977), rev den (1978), 281 Or 323.
